authors: Katherine Thurber, Anne-Marie Boxall, Krister Partel
citation.title: Overweight and obesity among Indigenous children: individual and social determinants

facebook.title: Overweight and obesity among Indigenous children: individual and social determinants
facebook.summary: Factors influencing obesity are not confined to the health portfolio, argues this paper. Instead the factors occur across portfolios including housing, education, employment, social welfare and community development.
